        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3976977718" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13269933176599156942">All three of the books in this trilogy are of the romance genre at their heart. However, they are all so well done (in the romance department) and mixed with a great adventure, they would suit most people who don&apos;t normally reach for romance. <br/><br/>If you enjoy fantasy, paranormal, and grand &apos;good vs. evil&apos; stories, this series should suit you very well. The romance actually enhances the story. <br/><br/>Thinking that Nora Roberts only wrote sappy romance novels, I have never picked one of her books up before b</span>
  <span id="freeText13269933176599156942" style="display:none">All three of the books in this trilogy are of the romance genre at their heart. However, they are all so well done (in the romance department) and mixed with a great adventure, they would suit most people who don't normally reach for romance. <br /><br />If you enjoy fantasy, paranormal, and grand 'good vs. evil' stories, this series should suit you very well. The romance actually enhances the story. <br /><br />Thinking that Nora Roberts only wrote sappy romance novels, I have never picked one of her books up before but will definitely reach for her books again! </span>
  <a data-text-id="13269933176599156942" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
